msgstr "*这需要使用标识符 '->' 以及输出下标标签列表。*"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:82 of
msgid "*identifier '->' as well as the list of output subscript labels.*"
msgstr "*此功能增强了函数的灵活性，因为可以在需要时禁用或强制求和。调用*"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:83 of
msgid "*This feature increases the flexibility of the function since*"
msgstr "*此功能增强了函数的灵活性，因为可以在需要时禁用或强制求和。调用*"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:84 of
