#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:86 of
msgid ""
"and ``mt.einsum('ii->i', a)`` is like :py:func:`mt.diag(a) "
"<maxframe.tensor.diag>`."
msgstr ""
"而 ``mt.einsum('ii->i', a)`` 类似于 :py:func:`mt.diag(a) <maxframe.tensor"
".diag>`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:87 of
msgid "The difference is that `einsum` does not allow broadcasting by default."
msgstr "区别在于 `einsum` 默认不允许广播。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:88 of
msgid "Additionally ``mt.einsum('ij,jh->ih', a, b)`` directly specifies the"
msgstr "此外，``mt.einsum('ij,jh->ih', a, b)`` 直接指定了"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:89 of
msgid "*order of the output subscript labels and therefore returns matrix*"
msgstr "输出下标标签的顺序，因此返回矩阵"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:90 of
