msgstr "乘法，与上面隐式模式的示例不同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:91 of
msgid "*To enable and control broadcasting, use an ellipsis.  Default*"
msgstr "要启用和控制广播，请使用省略号。默认"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:92 of
msgid "*NumPy-style broadcasting is done by adding an ellipsis*"
msgstr "NumPy 风格的广播是通过添加省略号"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:93 of
msgid "to the left of each term, like ``mt.einsum('...ii->...i', a)``."
msgstr "在每个项的左侧完成的，例如 ``mt.einsum('...ii->...i', a)``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:94 of
msgid "*To take the trace along the first and last axes,*"
msgstr "要沿第一个和最后一个轴取迹，"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:95 of
msgid "you can do ``mt.einsum('i...i', a)``, or to do a matrix-matrix"
msgstr "可以使用 ``mt.einsum('i...i', a)``，或者要做矩阵-矩阵"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:96 of
msgid "*product with the left-most indices instead of rightmost, one can do*"
msgstr "乘积但使用最左侧索引而不是最右侧索引，可以"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:97 of
msgid "``mt.einsum('ij...,jk...->ik...', a, b)``."
msgstr "使用 ``mt.einsum('ij...,jk...->ik...', a, b)``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:98 of
msgid "*When there is only one operand, no axes are summed, and no output*"
msgstr "当只有一个操作数、没有轴被求和且未提供输出"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:99 of
msgid "*parameter is provided, a view into the operand is returned instead*"
msgstr "参数时，将返回操作数的一个视图"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:100 of
msgid "of a new array.  Thus, taking the diagonal as ``mt.einsum('ii->i', a)``"
msgstr "而不是新数组。因此，将对角线提取为 ``mt.einsum('ii->i', a)``"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:101 of
msgid "*produces a view (changed in version 1.10.0).*"
msgstr "会产生一个视图（在 1.10.0 版本中更改）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:102 of
msgid "`einsum` also provides an alternative way to provide the subscripts"
msgstr "`einsum` 还提供了另一种提供下标的方式"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.einsum.einsum:103 of
msgid ""
"and operands as ``einsum(op0, sublist0, op1, sublist1, ..., "
